<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空离开之后，其他三人继续西行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天下午，他们停下来休息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒坐在路边的草地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打了个大大的哈欠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒。”唐僧说，“你去找点吃的来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净和我在这里等着。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒抱怨道：“哎！我刚坐下！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去西天太辛苦了。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完，他就走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒走了几分钟后，停下来四处看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>周围一个人都没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我太累了，没法去找吃的。”他自言自语地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我现在回去的话，师父会生气的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打了个哈欠。“我要睡一小会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等我睡醒了，我就回去跟师父说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我到处都走遍了，但是没找到吃的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒在灌木丛后面躺了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他就打起了呼噜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一个小时，唐僧和悟净依然在路边等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒怎么这么久还没回来？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净看上去有点儿生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说：“他可能找到了食物，正自己吃呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我去找找他。”悟净站起来，去找八戒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”一个声音突然响起，“面条，好吃！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净皱起了眉毛。“那是八戒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一定是找到了食物，但却不给我们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>与此同时，唐僧感觉有点儿无聊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他站起来伸了伸腿，四下看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这树林真美。”他自言自语地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去周边走走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧在树林中边走，边欣赏着花草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走到了树林深处。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在树林中央，他看到了一座宝塔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奇怪，这里有个宝塔。”他想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许，我们今晚可以在这里过夜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧走到宝塔门前，打开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他大吃一惊。有个妖怪正在里面睡觉！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪长了一脸紫色的胡子和一口锋利的尖牙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当唐僧想离开的时候，那个妖怪醒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁在那里？”妖怪大叫。他站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧转过身来，害怕得浑身发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很抱歉吵醒你了。”他说，“我，呃……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪走近了些，笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是个和尚。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪舔了舔自己的嘴唇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是，是。”唐僧说，“我来自大唐，我……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪的眼睛亮了。“你是唐僧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>与此同时，悟净顺着八戒的声音找了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在灌木丛背后找到了八戒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒在那里睡得正香。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能再给我一些豆腐吗？”八戒问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在说梦话。“好的，请多给点儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会把它们吃光的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净踢了八戒一脚，说：“醒醒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒跳了起来，擦了擦嘴角的口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们都在等着你，你居然在这里睡觉？”悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我们现在回去找师父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他低着头，跟着悟净往回走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们回来的时候，唐僧却不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许他在附近。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和八戒在树林里到处寻找唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>347588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他们就看到了那座宝塔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>347589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们敲了敲门。妖怪开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>353668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>357140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们是谁？”妖怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>357141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>359532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净告诉了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>359533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>363986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们正在找一个和尚。”妖怪笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>363987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>372716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我这里有个和尚。我要把他当晚饭吃！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>